OL,3,CPrince William has microfibre filter
OL,4,Cfitted to washing machines at home
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales arrived in Bristol
OL,7,Ftoday for a visit highlighting the
OL,8,Fcity's position at the forefront of
OL,9,Fsustainable technology and scientific
OL,10,Finnovation.
OL,12,FPrince William's first stop was at
OL,13,F'Matter', a Bristol-based company and
OL,14,F2025 Earthshot Prize finalist, where
OL,15,Fhe witnessed their groundbreaking
OL,16,Ffiltration technology designed to
OL,17,Fprevent microplastics from entering
OL,18,FBritain's waterways.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
