OL,3,CPrince William has microfibre filter
OL,4,Cfitted to washing machines at home
OL,6,FThe company demonstrated how their
OL,7,Fsystem captures harmful microfibres
OL,8,Fbefore they reach the water supply.
OL,10,FThe visit held particular
OL,11,Fsignificance, as founder Adam's
OL,12,Fentrepreneurial journey began with a
OL,13,F#250 grant from the Prince's Trust
OL,14,Fmore than eight years ago.
OL,16,FPrince William has already installed
OL,17,Fthe filtration system in his own
OL,18,Fhousehold, purchasing it at full
OL,19,Fprice, and the systems are now being
OL,20,Frolled out across all royal palaces.
