OL,3,CPrince William has microfibre filter
OL,4,Cfitted to washing machines at home
OL,6,FDuring a demonstration of machinery
OL,7,Fthat removes microfibres during
OL,8,Ftextile manufacturing, the Prince
OL,9,Fexpressed his dismay at the volume of
OL,10,Fwaste produced.
OL,12,F"I'm genuinely horrified," he said,
OL,13,Fwatching the waste accumulate. "It's
OL,14,Fabsolutely atrocious that we allow
OL,15,Fthat. Companies must have known how
OL,16,Fmuch stuff they are washing away."
OL,18,FThe Prince then travelled to the
OL,19,FUniversity of Bristol to visit
OL,20,FIsambard-AI, the UK's most powerful
OL,21,Fsupercomputer.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
