OL,3,CPrince William has microfibre filter
OL,4,Cfitted to washing machines at home
OL,6,FThe machine possesses extraordinary
OL,7,Fprocessing power, capable of
OL,8,Fcompleting in one second what would
OL,9,Ftake the entire human population 80
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FScientists demonstrated how the
OL,13,Fsupercomputer is being used to develop
OL,14,Ftreatments for heart disease,
OL,15,FAlzheimer's and cancer, as well as to
OL,16,Fpredict extreme weather events.
OL,18,FHis Royal Highness also viewed a
OL,19,Fparacanoe seat developed for
OL,20,FParalympic champion Emma Wiggs MBE,
OL,21,Fwho won gold and silver at Paris 2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
