OL,3,CPrince William has microfibre filter
OL,4,Cfitted to washing machines at home
OL,6,FThe innovative seat, made using
OL,7,Fdigital tools and embedded sensors, is
OL,8,Ffive times stiffer yet lighter than
OL,9,Ftraditional designs, significantly
OL,10,Fimproving power transfer and speed.
OL,12,FThe Prince concluded his visit by
OL,13,Fmeeting founders of two start-ups led
OL,14,Fby University of Bristol graduates,
OL,15,Fboth working to improve lives for
OL,16,Fpeople with disabilities and those
OL,17,Fliving with dementia.
